				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "All lines here should be short!\r\nSeveral posters can be found across the city announcing the impending execution of Florrick. With every longrest taken ever since the player party KNOWS about the execution we count down 1 day. When any poster is destroyed the funny addendum line is played as well. When the execution is bound to happen next day a rnadom party member reacts ONCE. Poster are gone when the execution happened. The posters claim the xecution is \"postponed\" when Florrick is saved from the prison."
				}
